{"tid":1802001,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家睇睇德國係WWII衰d咩，再諗下而家我地冒處境","createTime":"2019-12-29T05:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T06:32:50.000Z","uid":172599,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0eb3a7341fa41602a9d383dbb9b8a98793c01b","tid":1802001,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:58:27.000Z","msg":"德國係二戰既時候，因為有機動部隊既強大，因而好快咁攻下波蘭法國比利時等地<br />\n<br />\n而英國、俄羅斯都係佢地想攻打既地方<br />\n<br />\n係佢地空氣同坦克既強勢下，其實英國同俄羅斯，由其是俄羅斯，開頭都處於下風<br />\n<br />\n甚至俄羅斯比人打到差唔多去到首都，但最後都失敗左，點解？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1) 資源唔夠，開得太多戰線</span></span><br />\n- 德國以為自己同時可以應付西邊既英美法加，東邊既俄羅斯，其實係完全唔夠<br />\n同時，因為係開始既時候快速地得到多場勝利，失去左長期作戰既計劃，比如補給，前線既士氣同健康等，最後係對方人多同已方士氣低落既情況下係俄羅斯慘敗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2) 情報唔夠，錯估形勢</span></span><br />\n- 德國一直都唔太種視情報，或者無視一d情報，導致自high，到最後已經太遲。其實一直有一d零散既情資，但上級唔聽，一味堅持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">3) 最重要：死要面，唔識進退</span></span><br />\n- 希特拉最on9就係佢同日本人有d似，係可以退既時候唔退，因為覺得亞利安人唔係咁無尊嚴，最後導致東征俄羅斯既大軍白白地死守、投降，死左好多人。其實德軍係一早可以走，但就係因為咁on9既教條主義所以白白咁sacrifice。前線既將士都係，上級講既野唔敢反對，明明有自己思考但唔敢提出。<br />\n<br />\n講左d咩自己參透"},{"pid":"4bab13a77658def9d4c3848831aedaa5f193ed0c","tid":1802001,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3b42280b1bdd28366883d224601c6e5d59874bf","tid":1802001,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得係資訊，即係中間被英美偷左資訊<br />\n<br />\n所以美國而家搞華為，或者點解中國會整華為出黎"},{"pid":"1e0633fc87b0f700c4318050cb3810106e0f39ef","tid":1802001,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:04:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1717055cf7872c7b4c8ef11be35cf42669ce63a","tid":1802001,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"有集會啊 大家記得要去啊 熱門一個Po都冇 完全唔夠宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主可唔可以暫時頂置呢段嘢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vtmTubg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvtmTubg.jpg&h=fb1fd725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4291f60f52c194532df5d5d75429309074104178","tid":1802001,"uid":70147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"代入番落中國咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f215adbc7c36f7d9717fa7e32cad963267b3bd","tid":1802001,"uid":60749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"盟軍成功破解enigma都係致勝關鍵<br />\n盟軍知道德軍部署 行動<br />\n所有反制照住嚟打 開咗上帝視角"},{"pid":"e6d2f5cab2181a5f3774a9cf83a282a075c0bbdb","tid":1802001,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:25:19.000Z","msg":"共產黨都面對緊同一問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb338215c75f285281ff59488f710ddfdcb6da6","tid":1802001,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":